      <title>Triton Partners说，将在回收公司Befesa中建立股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/buyout-firm-triton-said-to-build-stake-in-recycling-firm-befesa</link>
      <description><![CDATA[熟悉此事的人们说，收购公司Triton Partners已在Befesa SA中建立了股份，这标志着五年前退出后的废物回收公司返回。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/buyout-firm-triton-said-to-build-stake-in-recycling-firm-befesa</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 16:03:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
