      <title>SEC优先审查未决的共同基金ETF应用程序</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/sec-to-prioritize-review-of-pending-mutual-fund-etf-applications</link>
      <description><![CDATA[代理证券和交易委员会主席马克·乌耶达（Mark Uyeda）希望监管机构在审查申请中更快地提出启动新颖的交易所资金，例如Dimensional Fund Advisors提出的申请。]]></description>
