    <item>
      <title>特朗普对新鲜的胡塞威胁加大对伊朗的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/trump-ramps-up-pressure-on-iran-with-fresh-houthi-threats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统对伊朗的压力施加了压力，要求他们遏制霍蒂斯（Houthis），如果激进组织不停止袭击，则提高了也门以外的报复罢工的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/trump-ramps-up-pressure-on-iran-with-fresh-houthi-threats</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 15:43:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>策略在宣布首选销售后购买更多比特币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/strategy-buys-more-bitcoin-after-announcing-preferred-offering</link>
      <description><![CDATA[迈克尔·塞勒（Michael Saylor）的策略表示，它在揭幕计划发行多达210亿美元的优先股以获取更多加密货币的计划后一周购买了1,070万美元的比特币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/strategy-buys-more-bitcoin-after-announcing-preferred-offering</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 12:14:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
